8\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite id=\"CITEREFCocchiaraConnerleyBell2010\" class=\"citation journal\">Cocchiara, Faye K.; Connerley, Mary L.; Bell, Myrtle P. (November\u2013December 2010). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://doi.org/10.1002/hrm.20396\">\"<span style=\"padding-left:0.2em;\">\"</span>A GEM\" for increasing the effectiveness of diversity training\"</a>. <i>Human Resource Management</i>. <a href=\"/wiki/Wiley-Blackwell\" title=\"Wiley-Blackwell\">Wiley</a>. <b>49</b> (6): 1089&#8211;1106. <a href=\"/wiki/Digital_object_identifier\" title=\"Digital object identifier\">doi</a>:<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"//doi.org/10.1002/hrm.20396\">10.1002/hrm.20396</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.jtitle=Human+Resource+Management&amp;rft.atitle=%22A+GEM%22+for+increasing+the+effectiveness+of+diversity+training&amp;rft.volume=49&amp;rft.issue=6&amp;rft.pages=1089-1106&amp;rft.date=2010-11%2F2010-12&amp;rft_id=info%3Adoi%2F10.1002%2Fhrm.20396&amp;rft.aulast=Cocchiara&amp;rft.aufirst=Faye+K.&amp;rft.au=Connerley%2C+Mary+L.&amp;rft.au=Bell%2C+Myrtle+P.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1002%2Fhrm.20396&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ADiversity+training\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Utz, Richard (January 18, 2017). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chronicle.com/article/The-Diversity-Questionthe/238914\">\"The Diversity Question in Administrative-Job Interviews\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Chronicle_of_Higher_